Package: StatRidge
Type: Package
Title: Ridge Regression Methods and Simulation Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Jerson",
      family = "Mohamad",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "mohamad.jerson@wmsu.edu.ph"
    )
Description: An R package translating peer-reviewed research on ridge
    regression estimation into reusable statistical software. StatRidge
    implements classical and proposed ridge regression methodologies for
    linear, logistic, and Poisson regression models together with
    simulation and model comparison tools for research, teaching, and
    statistical data analysis.
